title: RobberySetUp
body:
Driver: Hey buddy, are you interested in a good time? Maybe make some $$$ too?
[[You betcha'!|Yes]]
[[No thanks:)|No]]
[[Fuck off!|AgroNo]]

title: Yes
body:
CW: I'm in! Tell me more
Driver: I knew it! Take a right at the fork and follow me ahead.

title: No
body:
CW: No thanks, pal! Appreciate the offer though!
Driver: Don't be naive! I'll meet you up the road. Take a right at the fork ahead.

title: AgroNo
body:
CW: I don't know you!! Bugger off!
Driver: Hey easy there! Well if you change your mind Just swing a right at the fork up the road.
